reviewText: Everything NLP Comprehensive that I have seen is good I would like to see "Timelines" by Connirae but the DVD I got for "Timelines" was a misprint Also "Self Concept" by Steve This Program, It is good but I only need one copy I would like to see "Timelines" if I could get it The replacement was the same misprint I would like to see the one I ordered I do not need 3 copies of the one I have seen It is a good program but I only need one dvd I do not need 3 copies of the same program
It's a tape of a seminar.  The information is good but if you are going to make and sell a video, do a presentation for video with a little regard for being concise.
